      <title>首席财务官表示，XPO 希望降低杠杆率，并可能提前回购债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-12/logistics-firm-xpo-working-to-reduce-debt-could-buy-back-debt-early-cfo-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[物流提供商 XPO Inc. 财务主管表示，在从已倒闭的货运公司 Yellow Corp. 购买资产后，该公司正在努力降低杠杆率，并可能考虑按面值回购部分债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-12/logistics-firm-xpo-working-to-reduce-debt-could-buy-back-debt-early-cfo-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Feb 2024 15:46:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
